  "FDMMU-USA": {
    "about": "Freedom Metals Acquisition Corp. (FDMMU) is a special purpose acquisition company (SPAC) seeking to merge with a target company in the metals or mining industry. Through this merger, it aims to take a metals-focused business public, leveraging the SPAC structure to access capital for growth and expansion in the mining sector.",
