  "HEROFINCORP-India": {
    "about": "Hero Fincorp is a non-banking financial company (NBFC) and part of the Hero Group, primarily focused on financing two-wheeler purchases and other consumer durable products. The company operates through a diversified lending portfolio including retail financing, corporate lending, and small business loans. It leverages the Hero Group's extensive dealer network and brand recognition to source customers and manage credit risk.",
